# UI Design Principles for Aura

## Unique Visual Identity
- Establish a cosmic, immersive design language with a space-themed interface
- Use glow effects and subtle animations to create a premium, futuristic feel
- Implement custom UI components rather than standard ones

## Color Usage
- Primary background: Deep midnight blue (#0A0E1A) for an immersive experience
- Text and UI elements: Stardust white (#F0F0F0) for maximum readability
- Accent colors with meaning:
  - Fiery red (#FF3B30): Represents bullish trends, hawkish sentiment
  - Cool blue (#00A9E0): Represents bearish trends, dovish sentiment
  - Golden highlight (#FFD60A): Used for key elements and wealth indicators

## Typography & Layout
- Clean, readable typography with clear information hierarchy
- Spacious layouts with proper alignment and consistent spacing
- Card-based UI with subtle borders and backdrop blur effects

## Animation & Interaction
- Smooth transitions between screens and states
- Micro-interactions for better feedback (button presses, loading states)
- Custom scrolling effects and timeline animations
- Interactive charts with hover/touch effects

## Screen-Specific Design
- Market: Card-based layout with prominent charts
- Signals: Immersive visualization with particle effects
- Insights: Timeline-based news feed with clear chronology
- Settings: Organized list with colorful icons and clear categories
